e": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2014237129174164869"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIj7zp+byUvu1vEAMaCTExODY4Mjg5OSDihLjNBjAAOPkCQAtyEzIwMTQyMzcxMjkxNzQxNjQ4Njl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1773071962.384019", "card_id": "Q_2013404790034540313", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 380}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美以袭击伊朗进入第 10 天，当前局势如何？有哪些值得关注的信息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c7c96634cbddb734a3f1d93fc54b701d.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "81 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2013404790034540313"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIj7zp+byUvu1vEAMaCTExODY2MDEyOSC19qvNBjAAOLcIQAxyEzIwMTM0MDQ3OTAwMzQ1NDAzMTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1773071962.384266", "card_id": "Q_2012579639827063482", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 115}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "日本学者 Cell 子刊发文，首次证实「人可以经肛门呼吸」，相关研究有哪些应用场景和实际意义？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2025 年 12 月，武部贵则团队在 Cell 子刊 Med 发表题为「Safety and tolerability of intrarectal perfluorodecalin for enteral ventilation in a first-in-human trial」的临床研究文章。全氟萘烷（perfluorodecalin，PFD）是一种具有高氧溶解度的液体，能够作为液体氧载体，通过扩散驱动气体溶解和运输，实现经肛门肠内通气（EVA）技术。该研究评估了直肠给予 PFD 进行肠内通气的安全性和耐受性。其Ⅰ期临床试验首次评估了人体内直肠给予 PFD 的可行性，研究结果定义了一种新型辅助呼吸器官 —— 肠道，为 EVA 作为呼吸衰竭患者的辅助供氧手段提供可能。 此前，2024 年日本理工大学武部贵则研究团队发现了小鼠、大鼠和猪在内的哺乳动物可绕过呼吸系统，通过肛门呼吸，并被授予「搞笑诺贝尔奖」。%3Dihub"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d777ba6fb6435c8878acdb406b35ff47_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "79 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2012579639827063482"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIj7zp+byUvu1vEAMaCTExODYzMTY2OSC69Z/NBjAAOMgCQA1yEzIwMTI1Nzk2Mzk4MjcwNjM0ODJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1773071962.385371", "card_id": "Q_2011908777159389868", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "春招面试又被拒了，想问问大家，人生的容错率真的很高吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-97bee93d408967fdcbc319c7661123ec.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2011908777159389868"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIj7zp+byUvu1vEAMaCTExODYwODM4OCDvk5bNBjAAODNADnITMjAxMTkwODc3NzE1OTM4OTg2OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1773071962.385647", "card_id": "Q_2014375453297702712", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 145}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "伊朗外长表示不结束战争伊朗不会停火，如何解读这一表态？这场战事最终将走向何方？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当地时间 3 月 8 日，在美国全国广播公司《与新闻界对话》节目中，针对美国总统特朗普称「伊朗应为伊朗南部女子小学遭袭事件负责」一事，伊朗外长阿拉格齐回应称，这样的发言「很可笑」。阿拉格齐指出，是伊朗的学生、伊朗的女孩遭到了美国喷气式战斗机的袭击。这不是伊朗挑起的战争，不是伊朗攻击自己的人民——如果不是美国，那只能是以色列了。 2 月 28 日，美国联合以色列对伊朗发起军事行动，伊朗南部米纳卜市的一所小学遭袭，导致至少 165 人遇难，其中大多是 10 岁左右的小女孩。此前据美国有线电视新闻网（CNN）、路透社等媒体报道，目前证据显示，美国对伊朗小学遭袭事件负责的可能性越来越大。 此外，阿拉格齐强调，这次美以联合袭击伊朗与去年 6 月的「12 日战争」不同，上次伊朗善意接受停火，却并没有迎来和平。他表示，这次除非彻底结束战争，否则伊朗不接受美以提出的停火，伊朗会继续战斗以保护伊朗人民。伊朗外长说不止战伊朗不会停火"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-fac70d9edea173d4500ac8bb1a0ebc7a.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2014375453297702712"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIj7zp+byUvu1vEAMaCTExODY4OTgwNSC1hrrNBjAAOLIDQA9yEzIwMTQzNzU0NTMyOTc3MDI3MTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1773071962.386501", "card_id": "Q_1956100283072479667", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "库里、乔丹、奥尼尔、邓肯，你会选哪个作为核心建队？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-28788868e664d9e7bd526ee22a4e4f77_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1956100283072479667"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIj7zp+byUvu1vEAMaCTExNjc3ODIwNiC6hOrGBjAAOA9AEHITMTk1NjEwMDI4MzA3MjQ3OTY2N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1773071962.389494", "card_id": "Q_2010212483034531395", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "考试成绩与科研能力之间存在着什么联系？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "题主今年大四即将毕业，未来想进入科研领域工作。最近一直在思考一个问题：许多人进入科研领域的敲门砖是自己优异的成绩，这些成绩往往是以考试的形式进行评分的。然而真实的科研却和考试有很大的区别。不可否认的是成绩优秀的人似乎更可能科研出成果，但我总觉得两者之间存在一种矛盾：考试是要在有限的时间里去复现自己烂熟于心的知识和套路，这种急功近利的状态我认为是与科研相悖的：即便天才也需要时间去思考去推演去检查自己的研究成果，其背后也未必存在一个「正确答案」。所以我的问题是：在成绩超过某一个临界点后，成绩的高低是否会与科研能力呈负相关？（抱歉在车上写的问题描述有些粗糙）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-482c62c84353e27eea09a22e0db24d35_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area